-- China Railway to Raise Up to $914 Million to Fund Construction Projects
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-06-19T00:14:20Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-19/china-railway-to-raise-up-to-914-million-to-fund-construction-projects.html

          
          
             China Railway Group Ltd. plans to
raise as much as 6.24 billion yuan by selling up to 1.52 billion
new shares through a private placement, according to a company
filing to the Shanghai Stock Exchange.  
 It will use the funds for two construction projects in
Shenzhen and Liuzhou. China Railway Engineering Group Co., the
companyâ€™s biggest shareholder, plans to purchase up to 3.5
billion yuan of the new shares.  
          
          


  


        